name: Lava Arshola
description: These are always fun. I’ll start with I’m a single mom of two beautiful girls and I am in nursing school. To sum it up, I am a busy person with limited time. I love everything Disney and superheroes. Batman is the best. I’m a honest person. I like actual intellectual conversation, so if you’re the person who replies with “lol” or “k” a lot, please don’t waste my time. I have 5 tattoos and I plan to get many more. I’ll leave the rest for you to ask 🙂
